\c 9
\s Sauro anozodzwa naSamueri
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakange kuno murume waBhenjamini, wainzi Kishi, mwanakomana waAbhieri, mwanakomana waZerori, mwanakomana waBhekorati, mwanakomana waAfia, mwanakomana womuBhenjamini, munhu waiva nesimba noumhare.
\v 2 Uyu munhu wakange ano mwanakomana wainzi Sauro, jaya rakanaka; kwakange kusino umwe munhu pakati pavana vaIsraeri wakange akamukunda pakunaka; kubva pamafudzi ake kusvika kumusoro wake wakange akapfuura vanhu vese pakureba.
\v 3 Zvino mbongoro dzaKishi, baba vaSauro, dzakange dzarasi ika. Ipapo Kishi akati kuna Sauro, mwanakomana wake: Enda neumwe wavaranda, mundotsvaka mbongoro.
\v 4 Iye akapfuura nokunyika yamakomo yaEfuremu, akapfuurawo nokunyika yamakomo yeSharisha, asi havana kudziwana; zvino vakapfuurazve nokunyika yeSharimi, asi naipapo dzakange dzisipo; ipapo akapfuura nokunyika yavaBhenjamini, asi havana kudziwana.
\v 5 Zvino vakati vachisvika kunyika yeZufi, Sauro akati kumuranda wake, wakange anaye: Ngatidzoke hedu; baba vangu zvimwe vangarega kufunga mbongoro, vakafunganya pamusoro pedu.
\v 6 Iye akati kwaari: Tarirai, muguta rino muno munhu waMwari, munhu unokudzwa kwazvo; zvese zvaanotaura zvinoitika; hendei zvino ikoko, zvimwe ungatiudza nzira yatingafamba nayo.
\v 7 Zvino Sauro akati kumuranda wake: Asi tarira, kana tikaenda, tichanovigirei munhu uyo? Nokuti zvingwa zvakange zviri mumidziyo yedu zvapera; hapana chipo chatingavigira munhu waMwari; tineiko?
\v 8 Ipapo muranda akapindurazve, akati kuna Sauro: Tarirai, ndine chechina cheshekeri resirivha muruoko rwangu; ndichachipa munhu waMwari, atiudze nzira yedu.
\v 9 (Kare pakati paVaIsraeri kana munhu ondobvunza Mwari, waiti: Handei kuMuvoni; nokuti unonzi Muporofita zvino wainzi Muvoni kare).
\v 10 Ipapo Sauro akati kumuranda wake: Ishoko rakanaka, hendei. Naizvozvo vakaenda kuguta kwakange kuno munhu waMwari.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vakati vachikwira kuguta, vakasongana navasikana vakange vabuda kundoteka mvura, vakati kwavari: Muvoni ari pano here?
\v 12 Vakapindura, vakati: Aripo, tarirai, hoyo pamberi penyu; kurumidzai henyu zvino, nokuti wasvika muguta nhasi; nokuti vanhu vanobaira nhasi padunhu rakakwirira.
\v 13 Kana mangoti mapinda muguta, muchamuwana pakarepo achigere kukwira kudunhu rakakwirira kundodyapo; nokuti vanhu havangadyi, iye asati asvika, nokuti ndiye unoropafadza chibayiro; pashure ivo vakakokwa vachadya. Naizvozvo chikwirai zvino, nokuti muchamuwana nenguva ino.
\v 14 Ipapo vakakwira kuguta. Vakati vosvika muguta, vakaona Samueri obuda, akasangana navo okwira kudunhu rakakwirira.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Jehovha wakange azivisa Samueri zuva rakatangira kusvika kwaSauro, akati:
\v 16 Mangwana nenguva ino ndichatuma kwauri munhu unobva kunyika yaBhenjamini; unofanira kumuzodza, kuti ave mutungamiriri wavanhu vangu VaIsraeri aponese vanhu vangu mumaoko avaFirisitia; nokuti ndakatarira vanhu vangu, nokuti kuchema kwavo kwakasvika kwandiri.
\v 17 Zvino Samueri wakati achiona Sauro, Jehovha akati kwaari: Ndiye munhu wandakakuudza ndichiti: Ndiye uchabata vanhu vangu.
\v 18 Ipapo Sauro akaswedera kuna Samueri pasuwo, akati: Ndiudzeiwo kuti imba yoMuvoni iripi?
\v 19 Samueri akapindura Sauro, akati: Ndini Muvoni; nditungamirirei mukwire kudunhu rakakwirira, nokuti munofanira kudya neni nhasi; mangwana ndichakutendera kuenda, ndigokuudzawo zvese zviri pamoyo wako.
\v 20 Asi kana dziri mbongoro dzako dzakange dzarasi ika mazuva matatu, usadzifunga hako, nokuti dzatowanikwa hadzo. Asi zvese zvinodikanwa naIsraeri hazvizi kwauri here? Hazvizi kwauri nokuna vese veimba yababa vako here?
\v 21 Sauro akapindura, akati: Ko handizi muBhenjamini, worudzi rudiki kumarudzi ese aIsraeri here? Uye mhuri yangu haizi diki kumhuri dzese dzorudzi rwaBhenjamini here? Munotaurireiko kudaro kwandiri?
\v 22 Samueri akatora Sauro nomuranda wake, akapinda navo mumba mokudyira, akavagarisa pavakakudzwa kupfuura vamwe vakakokwa, vaiva vanhu vanenge makumi matatu.
\v 23 Zvino Samueri akati kumubiki: Uya nomugove wandakakupa ndichiti: Chiuchengeta uri woga.
\v 24 Mubiki akatora chidzva nezvese zvakange zviri pachiri, akazvigadza pamberi paSauro. Samueri akati: Tarira, ndicho chakange chakachengetwa; uzvigadze pamberi pako, udye, nokuti zvakakuchengeterwa iwe kusvikira nguva yakafanira, nokuti ndakati: Ndakokera vanhu. Naizvozvo Sauro akadya naSamueri musi iwoyo.
\p
\v 25 Zvino vakati vaburuka padunhu rakakwirira, vakapinda muguta, akataurirana naSauro padenga reimba.
\v 26 Vakamuka mangwanani, mambakwedza, Samueri akadana Sauro padenga reimba, akati: Muka, ndikuendise. Ipapo Sauro akamuka, vakabuda iye naSamueri vari vaviri.
\v 27 Zvino vakati voburuka pamugumo weguta, Samueri akati kuna Sauro: Raira muranda atungamire mberi kwedu (iye akatungamira hake); asi iwe chimbomira hako, ndikuzivise shoko raMwari.
